rows.label: qst650501_0040
rows.name: From the country he loved so much...

rows.label: qst650501_0050
rows.name: Where did all this data come from...?

rows.label: qst650501_0060
rows.name:
And such a wide-open battlefield, too.
Very realistic for a simulation...

rows.label: qst650501_0080
rows.name:
That Nopon trader really gave
me a good deal on this.

rows.label: qst650501_0100
rows.name: I see. So you're my enemies then.

rows.label: qst650501_0110
rows.name:
Only this many though? I'll have to tell
him to crank up the difficulty next time.

rows.label: qst650501_0120
rows.name:
Fortune favors the bold. I'll ambush
them with some ranged Arts...

rows.label: qst650501_0140
rows.name:
That put a dent in 'em. I'll move
in and keep the rhythm going!

rows.label: qst650501_0170
rows.name:
That voice-?! It doesn't
match Prone data...

rows.label: qst650501_0180
rows.name:
Is the simulator bugging out? Seems
best to clear them out quickly...
